Italy says Q1 PSBR 24 . 0 trillion lire . Italy ' s cumulative public sector borrowing requirement was around 24 . 0 trillion lire at end - March 1997 , compared with 46 . 324 trillion in the first quarter last year , the Treasury Ministry said in a statement . It said the borrowing requirement in March was 17 . 5 trillion lire , more than 3 . 0 trillion less than in March 1996 . The statement gave no further data but said the figures were worked out in accordance with a ruling in March by Eurostat , the EU ' s statistics body . - - Rome newsroom + 396 678 2501 
